        </section>
        <section id="testimonials">
            <div class="left">
                <p>Testimonials</p>
                <h2>What people say about our blog</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="right">
                <div class="testimonial-slideshow-container">
                    <!-- Full-width images with number and caption text -->
                    <div class="mySlides fade">
                        <div class="top">
                            <div class="text">As a car enthusiast, I've found the insights and reviews on CarInsights invaluable for staying up-to-date with the latest trends in the automotive industry. The expert tips have helped me optimize my driving experience, and the thorough car reviews have guided me in making informed decisions when purchasing my latest vehicle. I highly recommend CarInsights to anyone passionate about cars!</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bottom">
                            <img src="images/testimonial/jonathan.png">
                            <div class="details">
                                <div class="name">Jonathan Vallem</div>
                                <div class="city">New York,</div>
                                <div class="country">USA</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>              
                    </div>
                    <div class="mySlides fade">
                        <div class="top">
                            <div class="text">I stumbled upon CarInsights while researching electric vehicles, and I'm so glad I did! The detailed analysis of EV technology and reviews of different electric car models helped me make the switch to an EV with confidence. The blog's emphasis on sustainability and driving tips has also inspired me to adopt eco-friendly driving habits. Keep up the great work!</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bottom">
                            <img src="images/testimonial/david.png">
                            <div class="details">
                                <div class="name">David Smith</div>
                                <div class="city">Chennai,</div>
                                <div class="country">India</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>              
                    </div>
                    <div class="mySlides fade">
                        <div class="top">
                            <div class="text">As a busy professional, I don't always have the time to research every aspect of car maintenance and technology. Thankfully, CarInsights has become my go-to resource for staying informed about the latest car trends and getting practical tips for optimizing my driving experience. The content is well-researched, easy to understand, and always relevant to my needs. I wouldn't trust any other source for car advice!</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bottom">
                            <img src="images/testimonial/john.png">
                            <div class="details">
                                <div class="name">John Doe</div>
                                <div class="city">Mumbai,</div>
                                <div class="country">India</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>              
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Next and previous buttons -->
                    <a class="prev" onclick="plusSlides(-1)">&#10094;</a>
                    <a class="next" onclick="plusSlides(1)">&#10095;</a>
                  </div>
                  <br>
                  
                  <!-- The dots/circles -->
                  <div style="text-align:center">
                    <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(1)"></span>
                    <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(2)"></span>
                    <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(3)"></span>
                  </div>
            </div>
        </section>
